apscheduler==3.6.3


When the server start schedulers should be created for the auctions deadlines.

The schedulers should execute the method that resolve a particular auction.

The resolve method should pick a winner and notify by email the persons that should be notified.

Maybe hints:
https://medium.com/@bencleary/django-scheduled-tasks-queues-part-1-62d6b6dc24f8
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/47633704/execute-task-on-specific-time-in-django